Phyllis Brooks https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phyllis_Brooks 0 Phyllis Brooks (July 18, 1915 – August 1, 1995) was an American actress and model. She was born in Boise, Idaho. Some sources have also inaccurately cited 1914 as her year of birth, but 1915 is the correct year according to Social Security records.
